title.en_US: International Day to End Impunity for Crimes against Journalists
title.fa_IR: روز جهانی پایان دادن به مصونیت از مجازات جنایات علیه روزنامه‌نگاران

description.en_US: The International Day to End Impunity for Crimes against Journalists is a UN-recognized day observed annually on 2 November.
